title: What is the Greatest Song of All Time? | Double Header: The Struts and Marcus King | 1960s Old Crow
itunes:title: What is the Greatest Song of All Time? | Double Header: The Struts and Marcus King | 1960s Old Crow
description:
Backstage at Louder Than Life and Bourbon & Beyond, The Struts and Marcus King join Fred at his Jack Shack bar set up. The Struts lead singer Luke Spiller defends his recent comments about Queen, while Marcus King may have given a whole new meaning to the bourbon brand Smoke Wagon. 

What they sipped. The Struts: Jim Beam Legacy 15-Year. Marcus King: 1960s Old Crow Traveler Bottle, Smoke Wagon 2 Hot 4 Retail, 2022 Garrison Brothers Guadalupe 

Check out my event Blind Bourbon in Washington, DC, at Nationals Park
